WEBVTT

00:00:55.556 --> 00:01:00.472
a hostile border into dangerous,
uncharted territory.

00:01:00.496 --> 00:01:02.967
The world was suddenly
in this terrifying new place,

00:01:02.991 --> 00:01:05.485
and I was in this place as a new mother.

00:01:05.509 --> 00:01:08.334
I remember my thoughts
kind of ping-ponging around

00:01:08.358 --> 00:01:11.073
from, "How am I ever
going to protect this baby?"

00:01:11.097 --> 00:01:13.884
to, "How am I ever
going to get some sleep?"

00:01:14.728 --> 00:01:17.708
Well, my son turned 18 this year,

00:01:17.732 --> 00:01:22.423
along with millions of other people
who were babies on 9/11.

00:01:23.058 --> 00:01:24.244
And in that time,

00:01:24.268 --> 00:01:29.781
we have all crossed into this hostile,
uncharted territory

00:01:29.805 --> 00:01:31.775
of climate breakdown,